<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 33 (July 29th, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The tooltip on this item has been updated to calculate and show the amount of true damage your auto-attacks will deal.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32 (July 9th, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The true damage applied by this item's Unique Passive: Puncture will now calculate its damage before your target's mitigation is applied instead of afterwards.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 31 (June 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The true damage dealt by the Puncture Unique Passive has been increased to 10%, up from 5%.</li><li>The price of this item has been increased to 3000, up from 2190.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The Unique Passive - Puncture has been reworked.</li><li>Unique Passive - Puncture: Your basic attacks will deal an additional 5% of their damage as true damage.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 10 (August 23, 2013)</h4><ul><li>The Puncture passive ability on this item has been redesigned. Puncture now causes your next basic attack to deal bonus true damage every 3 seconds, this is changed from dealing bonus true damage ever 3rd attack.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 9 (August 15, 2013)</h4><ul><li>The cost of this item has been increased to 2850, up from 2830.</li><li>The amount of Haste this item gives has been reduced to 50, down from 65.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 3 (June 21, 2013)</h4><i>Developer Note: The range increase combined with the root was too effective on a single item at shutting down melee characters.</i><ul><li>The Netherbind passive from Insight has been moved to the new item: Duress. In the place of Netherbind is a new passive: Puncture.</li><li>Puncture - Puncture causes every third attack to deal bonus true damage, scaling off of a power ratio.</li><li>The amount of Haste granted by Insight has been increased to 65, up from 5</li></ul>